               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     5ra-60ra) 
 I-1) Introduction (fols. 5ra-7ra) 
 I-2) Homily by Timothy
                     (Damātewos), [Patriarch] of Alexandria [for Ḫǝdār] (fols. 7ra-12ra); miracle
                     (fol. 12ra-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 12vb-13ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     13ra-rb) 
 I-3) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox for the 12th
                     of Tāḫśāś [Miyāzyā] (fols. 13rb-16rb); miracle (fols. 16rb-17ra); commemorative
                     notice (fol. 17ra-rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 17rb-va) 
 I-4) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for the 12th of Ṭǝrr [Tāḫśāś] (fols. 17va-21va); miracle (fol.
                     21va-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 21vb-22ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 22ra-rb)
                     
 I-5) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Yakkātit (fols.
                     22rb-24rb); miracle (fol. 24rb-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 24vb-25ra);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fol. 25ra-rb) 
 I-6) Homily by Yoḥannǝs [Severus], Metropolitan
                     [Patriarch] of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 25rb-34va); miracle
                     (fols. 34va-35rb); commemorative notice (fol. 35rb) 
 I-7) Homily [by
                     Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the 12th of Miyāzyā [Ṭǝrr] (fols.
                     35va-39rb); miracle (fols. 39rb-40rb); commemorative notice (fol. 40rb-va);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fol. 40va) 
 I-8) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia
                     for Gǝnbot (fols. 40va-41vb); miracle (fols. 41vb-42va); commemorative notice
                     (fol. 42va-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fols. 42vb-43ra) 
 I-9) Homily by Yoḥannǝs,
                     Metropolitan of ʾAksum (ʾAkʷǝsǝm) for Sane (fols. 43ra-46vb); miracle (fols.
                     46vb-47vb); commemorative notice (fols. 47vb-48rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 48rb)
                     
 I-10) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs for Ḥamle (fols. 48rb-51rb);
                     miracle (fol. 51rb-vb); commemorative notice (fols. 51vb-52ra); ʾarke-hymn
                     (fol. 52ra-rb) 
 I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for Naḥāse (fols.
                     52rb-54rb); miracle (fol. 54rb-vb); commemorative notice (fol. 54vb);
                     ʾarke-hymn (fol. 55ra) 
 I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for Maskaram
                     (fols. 55ra-56va); miracle (fol. 56va-vb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     56vb-57ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 57ra) 
 I-13) Homily by an anonymous author
                     for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 57ra-59rb); miracle (fol. 59rb-va); commemorative notice
                     (fols. 59va-60ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 60ra) 
 II) Malkǝʾa Mikāʾel "Image of
                     Michael" (fols. 60rb-63ra) 
 III) Unidentified text (fol.
                     63rb-vb).</summary>
