                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; parts of the
                           names of the donors; groups of lines on the incipit pages of Texts I-1
                           and I-2; incipits of all sections and subsections; elements of the
                           punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">It cannot be excluded that Text III was
                        written in a different
                        hand.</handNote>
